            "body": "Run 'bin/yarn waitrm', then just wait RM to come back, and press 'Enter' to clear the flag and exit.\n\nIn the patch, the warit RM flag is a EPHEMERAL znode, when the ZK session closed, it will disappear, then YARN admin would not forget to clear the flag. Thanks for [~junping_du] 's suggestion.",
